 *
 * @param {Map<string>} emailDetails  Information needed to populate email body.
 * @return {string}  HTML code for email.
 *
 * @author [Andrey Gonzalez](<andrey.gonzalez@mail.mcgill.ca>)
 * @date  Oct 29, 2024
 * @update  Jan 15, 2025
 *
